@BaseUrl = {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}

### Echo chat — happy path: response should have role=assistant and content="echo: hi"
POST {{BaseUrl}}/v1/echo/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "s1",
  "message": "hi"
}


### Echo chat with a custom trace id — X-Trace-Id should be echoed in the response headers
POST {{BaseUrl}}/v1/echo/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-Trace-Id: trace-echo-001

{
  "session_id": "demo-session",
  "message": "what is the dosage of Rocefin?"
}


### Echo chat — validation 422 (empty message violates min_length=1)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/v1/echo/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "s1",
  "message": ""
}
